     <div class="single"> 
      <h1>杰克逊梦幻庄园将被出售 标价1亿美元</h1> 
      <div class="meta singlemeta"> 
       <span>2015-05-31 19:03</span> 
       <span> </span> 
       <span></span> 
       <span class="cmts"><a href="http://www.ccnovel.com/69941.html#comments" class="ds-thread-count" data-thread-key="69941">5个评论</a></span> 
       <span>字号: <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="mfbig">大</a> <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="mfmid">中</a> <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="mfsml mfcurrent">小</a> </span> 
      </div> 
      <!-- PostContent begin --> 
      <div class="entry"> 
       <div class="entrycontent fontsml"> 
        <!-- SingleAd begin --> 
        <!-- SingleAd end --> 
        <p><a href="http://img.ccnovel.com/2015/05/W020150531187452826392.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-69944" src="http://img.ccnovel.com/2015/05/W020150531187452826392.jpg" alt="W020150531187452826392" width="550" height="341" /></a></p> 
        <p>苏富比拍卖行与希尔顿海兰公司称，有关杰克逊的痕迹已经多数被抹去，这个占地11平方公里的游乐园被改造成宏伟院落。</p> 
        <p><a href="http://img.ccnovel.com/2015/05/W020150531187453467241.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-69945" src="http://img.ccnovel.com/2015/05/W020150531187453467241.jpg" alt="W020150531187453467241" width="550" height="360" /></a></p> 
        <p>《华尔街日报》报道称，偿还杰克逊债务的公司已经对“梦幻庄园”进行重新整修，最终将其上市出售。</p> 
        <div class="wumii-hook"> 
